children.text: Enough Said spoken word series event held at Bistro 4 (4040 St. Laurent, Montreal, QC, H2W 1Y8, Canada) on April 17, 1995, hosted by Lee Gotham. Feature performance by Clifton Joseph. Open mic/supporting performances by Norman Nawrocki, Justin McGrail, Steve "Liquid" Hawley, David Jager, Steve Godin and more.
